# Phase 212.H.7 — top-level Kconfig aggregator.
#
# PX4's external-modules walker reads `<EXTERNAL_MODULES_LOCATION>/src/Kconfig`
# and sources every per-module Kconfig it finds. `nros codegen-system
# --ahead-of-vendor --target px4` rewrites this file in-place with one
# `source` line per `[[component]]` from the bringup pkg's system.toml.
#
# Default: empty — `make px4_sitl_default` with an unpopulated nros
# template still configures cleanly. The first `nros codegen-system`
# run replaces this comment block with the per-component sources.
#
